✨ Features

Full Admin Panel GUI
Access all admin tools through an intuitive, beautiful GUI interface!

Player Management
- View and manage all online players
- View player inventory (editable!)
- Access player enderchest
- Heal, feed, teleport players
- Apply potion effects
- Manage economy
- Toggle fly, god mode, vanish
- Freeze/unfreeze players
- View player statistics
- Issue punishments

Server Management
- Time control (day, night, custom)
- Weather control (clear, rain, storm)
- Kill hostile mobs
- Remove entities (items, arrows, etc.)
- Broadcast messages
- Execute console commands
- Teleport all players
- View server info (TPS, players, version)

Economy Integration (Vault)
- View player balance
- Set exact balance
- Add/remove money
- Quick action buttons ($100, $1k, $10k)
- Reset balance

Potion Effects System
- 25+ potion effects available
- Apply to yourself or other players
- Clear all effects instantly
- Configurable duration and amplifier

⚔️ Punishment System
- Warning system with thresholds
- Auto-kick after X warnings
- Auto-ban after X warnings
- View punishment history
- Mute system
- Pre-configured templates

⚙️ Custom Commands
- Create custom GUI commands
- Execute as player or console
- Full placeholder support
- Icon customization

Staff Communication
- Staff Chat - Private communication channel for staff members
- Broadcast - Server-wide announcements with formatting

Admin Commands
Over 25+ admin commands for complete server control!

Multi-Language Support
10 languages included out of the box:
- English (en_US)
- Spanish (es_ES)
- Portuguese (pt_BR)
- German (de_DE)
- French (fr_FR)
- Chinese (zh_CN)
- Russian (ru_RU)
- Japanese (ja_JP)
- Korean (ko_KR)
- Italian (it_IT)

Plugin Integrations
- Vault - Full economy support
- PlaceholderAPI - Custom placeholders
- bStats - Anonymous metrics
